*------------------------------- *Consistency Equations* -------------------------------*
*‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾*
icc = 1
* DESCRIPTION:   Beta Consistency
* JUSTIFICATION: Consistency equations should always be on
* VARIABLES:     Calculated in-situ, no iteration variables

icc = 2
* DESCRIPTION:   Global Power Balance Consistency
* JUSTIFICATION: Consistency equations should always be on
* VARIABLES:     p_hcd_injected_total_mw, Rest calculated in-situ

icc = 11
* DESCRIPTION:   Radial Build Consistency
* JUSTIFICATION: Consistency equations should always be on
* VARIABLES:     rmajor, Rest calculated in-situ

