aspect = 1.8
*boundl(1) = 
*boundu(1) = 
* DESCRIPTION:   Aspect ratio
* JUSTIFICATION: 

*~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

*icc = 21
* DESCRIPTION:   Constraint equation for plasma minor radius lower limit 
* JUSTIFICATION: Turned off, don't care about lower limit
* VARIABLES:     rminor_min (minimum minor radius (m)), rminor calculated in-situ

*rminor_min = 0 
* DESCRIPTION:   Minimum minor radius (m) (icc=21)
* JUSTIFICATION: Not used, using a defined minor radius

*~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

i_plasma_geometry = 0
* DESCRIPTION:   Switch for plasma shape vs. aspect (default = 0)
* =0 use input kappa, triang to calculate 95% values
* =1 scale q95_min, kappa, triang with aspect ratio (ST)
* =2 set kappa to the natural elongation value (Zohm ITER scaling), triang input
* =3 set kappa to the natural elongation value (Zohm ITER scaling), triang95 input
* =4 use input kappa95, triang95 to calculate separatrix values
* =5 use input kappa95, triang95 to calculate separatrix values based on MAST scaling (ST)
* =6 use input kappa, triang to calculate 95% values based on MAST scaling (ST)
* =7 use input kappa95, triang95 to calculate separatrix values based on fit to FIESTA (ST)
* =8 use input kappa, triang to calculate 95% values based on fit to FIESTA (ST)
* =9 set kappa to the natural elongation value, triang input
* =10 set kappa to maximum stable value at a given aspect ratio (2.6<A<3.6)), triang input
* =11 set kappa Menard 2016 aspect-ratio-dependent scaling, triang input 
* JUSTIFICATION: Not set, assuming default value

kappa = 2.8
* DESCRIPTION:   Plasma Separatrix Elongation
* JUSTIFICATION:  

*kappa95 = 
* DESCRIPTION:   Plasma 95% elongation
* JUSTIFICATION: Not set, calculated as i_plasma_geometry=0 

triang = 0.5 
* DESCRIPTION:   Plasma Separatrix Triangularity
* JUSTIFICATION: 

*triang95 = 
* DESCRIPTION:   Plasma 95% triangularity
* JUSTIFICATION: Not set, calculated as i_plasma_geometry=0

*fkzohm = 
* DESCRIPTION:   Zohm elongation scaling multiplier (i_plasma_geometry 2,3)
* JUSTIFICATION: Not scaling plasma shape. Used when i_plasma_geometry=2,3

*m_s_limit =
* DESCRIPTION:   Margin to vertical stability (i_plasma_geometry = 10)
* JUSTIFICATION: Not used, not using i_plasma_geometry=10

*f_vol_plasma = 1.0
* DESCRIPTION:   Plasma volume multiplier
* JUSTIFICATION: Not scaling plasma volume

*~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

*icc = 23
* DESCRIPTION:   Constraint equation for conducting shell radius / rminor upper limit (FW) 
* JUSTIFICATION: Turned off, don't care about shell radius ratio limit for vertical stability
* VARIABLES:     f_r_conducting_wall calculated in-situ

*f_r_conducting_wall = 
* DESCRIPTION:   Max conducting shell to rminor radius
* JUSTIFICATION: Not using icc = 23

