*beta_vol_avg_min = 
* DESCRIPTION:   Plasma beta lower limit
* JUSTIFICATION: Turned off, not in use, Used with icc=84 to enforce beta limit

*~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

*beta_poloidal_max = 
* DESCRIPTION:   Maximum poloidal beta (`constraint equation 48`) (default = 0.19)
